<table border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="0" width="100%"></td></tr><tr><td class="article-table">Been stomping about the planes killing pretty much anything we could find - Aerin, Terris, Clockwork Dragon down in one day, took a shot at Behemoth too but he decided to warp up to the roof where we couldn't get at him. Also explored Crypt of Decay a little, knocked over Paffa and Carprim as well as some named rat guy. I think we managed to slip in another killing of Grummus in there also. Must be said, with the exception of Carprin (think AoW with a 3500 lifetap proc.. with no loot), all these encounters have been very well designed. Hopefully we'll get another shot at Behemoth soon, pretty disappointing to go through the trouble to spawn him and not even get a chance to actually fight him. I won't bore you with more aimless rambling here, the pictures speak for themselves:<br />
