	<table cellpadding='5' cellspacing='0' border='0'width='100%' bgcolor='#0d004c'>
	<tr><td><span style='color:#ffffff;font-weight:bold'>How do you spell Farm?</span></td></tr>
	</table><br/>
<table border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="0" width="100%"></td></tr><tr><td class="article-table">Here at Lotus Cult we spell it <I>V e x  T h a l</I>. We cleared through to Aten again after yet another wonderful patch full of astoundingly pointless bard nerfs, stepping out only briefly for a quick trip to the temple of snakes to take down creator and, once again, the emp. Not much else of note to report - server is currently down for maintenance, so we get to do it alllll over again next week!<br />
