<HR SIZE=1><br />
<br />
As mentioned above, we also stepped out to pay a visit to a couple of snakes in the temple of ssraeshza. I wasn't there for either - screenshots are courtesy of some other guild photographers - but I'm told both fights went smoothly as usual. Emp was kind enough to give us our first monk stick, as well as putting out a shawl of awakenings, one of his rarer drops for us.<br />
