<table border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="0" width="100%"></td></tr><tr><td class="article-table"><img src="http://acrego.homestead.com/files/vt/vttrain.JPG"></img><br />
<br />
Yeah so we started out in VT and got a few kills.  Thanks everyone for the ring of rage, it's kickass!  So we were clearing onward after TVK but oops, we got a train!  I know what you are saying... OMG NO!  A train in VT? WTF! No really, its actually true.  Sadly the nature and timing of the wipeout made CR impossible and restarting not an option :(<br />
<br />
So, we took a crew to ST to see whats up with that zone.  Pretty neat place but boy did it get a lot more crowded!  Anyway, we killed 3 of the new fangled warders, they dropped stuff, people looted it, heres a screenshot!  Sorry if its toobig (omg memories).  Anyway... I had a great time in ST, thanks for sticking with it those who stayed up until whatever friggin time it is.  My eyes so tired cant read clock~<br />
<br />
<img src="http://acrego.homestead.com/files/newst.JPG"></img><br />
<br />
I know theres been a lot more going on, but wanted to post this since I can yo!<br /><br /></td></tr></table><br/>

	<table cellpadding='5' cellspacing='0' border='0'width='100%' bgcolor='#0d004c'>
	<tr><td><span style='color:#ffffff;font-weight:bold'>VT Cleared!</span></td></tr>
	</table><br/>
<table border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="0" width="100%"></td></tr><tr><td class="article-table">As promised, we headed back into VT earlier in the week to clean up all the remaining bosses. The main mob of interest was Xundraux, who we hadn't killed before, and who turned out to be well worth the time spent clearing. We also finally managed to get both of the aten blobs dead at the same time, and they put out some nice stuff as a reward.<br />
<br />
